---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const canonical = 'https://webutilbox.com/privacy-policy';
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Privacy Policy | Webutilbox"
    description="Privacy Policy for Webutilbox - Learn how we handle your data and protect your privacy."
    canonical={canonical}
    keywords="privacy policy, webutilbox privacy, data protection, GDPR, CCPA"
>
    <header>
        <div class="header-content">
            <a href="/" class="logo">
                <span>🧰</span>
                <span>Webutilbox</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--primary);">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p style="font-style: italic; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 30px;">Last Updated: June 12, 2026</p>

        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">Welcome to Webutilbox. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we handle your information when you use our website and tools.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">1.1 Information You Provide</h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">Our tools work entirely in your browser. We do not collect, store, or transmit any data you input into our tools. All processing happens locally on your device.</p>

        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">1.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">When you visit our website, we may automatically collect:</p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Browser type and version</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Operating system</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">IP address (anonymized)</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Pages visited and time spent</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Referring website</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">We use the automatically collected information to:</p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Improve our website and tools</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Analyze usage patterns and trends</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Detect and prevent technical issues</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
        
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">3.1 Essential Cookies</h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">We use essential cookies to ensure our website functions properly. These cookies are necessary for basic functionality and cannot be disabled.</p>

        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">3.2 Analytics Cookies</h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">We may use analytics services to understand how visitors use our website. These services may use cookies to collect anonymous usage data.</p>

        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">3.3 Advertising Cookies</h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">We use Google AdSense to display advertisements on our website. Google AdSense uses cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to our website or other websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--primary); text-decoration: underline;">Google's Ads Settings</a>.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">4.1 Google AdSense</h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google may use cookies and web beacons to collect information about your visits to this and other websites to provide relevant advertisements. For more information about Google's privacy practices, please visit the <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--primary); text-decoration: underline;">Google Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

        <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">4.2 Content Delivery Networks (CDN)</h3>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">We use CDNs to deliver JavaScript libraries and other resources. These services may collect usage data according to their own privacy policies.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">5. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">Since our tools work entirely in your browser:</p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Your data never leaves your device</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">We do not store your files or inputs on our servers</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">All processing is done locally in your browser</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Your data is automatically cleared when you close the browser tab</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">6. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Access the information we collect about you</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Opt out of personalized advertising</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Disable cookies in your browser settings</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Request information about how we use your data</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">Our website is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">8. International Data Transfers</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">Our website is hosted on Netlify and may be accessed from anywhere in the world. By using our website, you consent to the transfer of your information to countries outside your country of residence, which may have different data protection laws.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">9. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date. We encourage you to review this privacy policy periodically.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">10. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external sites. We encourage you to read the privacy policies of any third-party sites you visit.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">11. Do Not Track Signals</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">Some browsers include a "Do Not Track" (DNT) feature. Our website does not currently respond to DNT signals, but we respect your privacy choices and provide options to control cookies and tracking.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">12. Data Retention</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">Since we do not collect or store user-generated data from our tools, there is no data retention period. Analytics data may be retained according to our analytics provider's policies.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">13. Contact Us</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us:</p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Email: <a href="mailto:innovativeme.dev@gmail.com" style="color: var(--primary); text-decoration: underline;">innovativeme.dev@gmail.com</a></li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Website: <a href="https://webutilbox.com/" style="color: var(--primary); text-decoration: underline;">webutilbox.com</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">14. GDPR Compliance (For EU Users)</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), you have additional rights under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR):</p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to access your personal data</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to rectification of inaccurate data</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to restrict processing</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to data portability</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to object to processing</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to withdraw consent</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">15. California Privacy Rights (CCPA)</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">If you are a California resident, you have specific rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA):</p>
        <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to know what personal information is collected</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to know if personal information is sold or disclosed</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to opt-out of the sale of personal information</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to deletion of personal information</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6;">Right to non-discrimination for exercising your rights</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary);">16. Consent</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--gray);">By using our website, you consent to our privacy policy and agree to its terms.</p>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
